Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 24
Set Width 1400
Set Height 750
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 32
Set PlaybackSpeed 1
Set TypingSpeed 75ms
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set BorderRadius 10
Set WindowBarSize 40
Set MarginFill "#1e1e2e"
Set Margin 20

Type "cd demo-files"
Enter
Sleep 300ms

Type "ls -1"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "npx diagram-sync"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 10s

Type "ls -1 diagrams"
Enter
Sleep 2s
